pers going forward d epartment chair 2011 12 jonathan levin jdlevin stanford edu vice chair 2011 12 liran einav leinav stanford edu undergraduate studies 2011 12 director of undergraduate study han hong doubleh stanford edu associate director of undergraduate study matt harding mch stanford edu introductory economics center john taylor johntayl stanford edu honors program geoffrey rothwell rothwell stanford edu undergraduate policy committee chair han hong graduate studies 2011 12 director of graduate study monika piazzesi piazzesi stanford edu graduate placement officer kyle bagwell kbagwell stanford edu graduate policy committee chair monika piazzesi graduate admissions bob hall rehall gmail com recruitment of admitted students pascaline dupas and nick bloom nbloom stanford edu search committees junior faculty recruiting chair pete klenow and martin schneider facilities and resources up maps and directions stanford university economics department 579 serra mall stanford ca 94305 6072 650 725 3266 all rights reserved terms of use contact
